Import vendors.csv
$ mongoimport --db trydb --collection vendors --type csv --headerline --drop --file vendors.csv

Import train_customers.csv
$ mongoimport --db trydb --collection customers --type csv --headerline --drop --file train_customers.csv

Import processed_orders.csv
mongoimport --db trydb --collection orders --type csv --headerline --drop --file processed_orders.csv


Index for Query 1:

db.vendors.createIndex({location: "2dsphere"}) 



Index for Query 2:

db.vendors.ensureIndex({"vendor_tag_name": "text"}, 
{"name": "tag_text", "default_language": "en", "language_override": "en"})
